WEBVTT
NOTE OE3D — Script4 — Hmoob

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:03.164
Zoo siab tuaj txog peb lub chaw kho mob, Ortho Espace 3D!

2
00:00:03.114 --> 00:00:06.123
Koj tau teem caij rau thawj zaug ntsib peb.

3
00:00:06.123 --> 00:00:09.428
Nov yog cov kauj ruam ntawm koj txoj kev ntsib no.

4
00:00:10.828 --> 00:00:12.526
Kev txais tos thiab kev tshuaj ntsuam.

5
00:00:12.476 --> 00:00:22.031
Koj tus kws kho mob pib nrog kev tshuaj ntsuam tag nrho: mloog koj qhov xav tau, tshuaj ntsuam koj lub cev thiab kev txav, thiab sib tham txog koj lub hom phiaj txhua hnub.

6
00:00:23.431 --> 00:00:25.139
Kev ntsuas.

7
00:00:25.089 --> 00:00:30.842
Raws li koj lub cuab yeej, peb ua ib lub qauv qub los yog kev ntsuas 3D siab heev.

8
00:00:30.842 --> 00:00:35.598
Koj koom nrog xaiv cov ntaub ntawv thiab cov khoom kom haum zoo rau koj.

9
00:00:36.998 --> 00:00:39.162
Kev ua raws li kev ntsuas.

10
00:00:39.112 --> 00:00:42.894
Koj lub cuab yeej raug tsim thiab ua hauv peb lub tsev ua hauj lwm hauv Guyane.

11
00:00:42.894 --> 00:00:45.606
Lub sijhawm nruab nrab yog ob txog plaub lub lis piam.

12
00:00:45.606 --> 00:00:51.548
Peb siv cov txheej txheem tshiab tshaj: luam 3D, kub hloov thiab kev kho raws tus kheej.

13
00:00:52.948 --> 00:00:55.020
Kev sim hnav thiab kev saib xyuas.

14
00:00:54.970 --> 00:00:59.829
Tom qab ua tiav, peb sim hnav los xyuas kev zoo thiab kev ua hauj lwm.

15
00:00:59.829 --> 00:01:02.513
Kev kho me ntsis raug ua hauv chaw.

16
00:01:02.513 --> 00:01:06.587
Kev saib xyuas tsis tu ncua raug teem rau ib hlis, ces txhua rau lub hlis.

17
00:01:07.987 --> 00:01:14.113
Peb lub chaw kho mob, Ortho Espace 3D, nrog koj txij thawj zaug ntsib mus txog kev saib xyuas ntev.

18
00:01:14.063 --> 00:01:18.194
Teem caij hnub no ntawm Cayenne, Kourou los yog Saint-Laurent-du-Maroni.
